979
01:29:42,200 --> 01:29:43,700
ainda vivos.

980
01:29:53,700 --> 01:29:54,900
Eu atendo.

981
01:29:59,200 --> 01:30:00,800
Graças a Deus!

982
01:30:01,000 --> 01:30:03,500
Encontraram-no, Donna.

983
01:30:03,800 --> 01:30:06,200
Dá-me um segundo...

984
01:30:06,700 --> 01:30:09,400
